@{
	ViewData["Title"] = "Join Our Team as a Trainer";
}
<div class="py-5" style="background-color: #5947ab;">
    <div class="container d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
        <div class="text-start textMain" style="max-width: 50%;">
            <h2 class="text-40 fw-bold text-yellow mb-3">FREE AND LIMITLESS EDUCATION WITH KODLA</h2>
            <p class="text-22 fw-medium mb-4">Break free from unchanging, boring curriculums and create your own system. Experience the excitement and joy of providing education freely while earning.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-light rounded fw-bold fs-6 py-3 px-4 textLightPurple" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Register">Become Our Trainer</a>
            @* <button asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Register" class="btn btn-light rounded fw-bold fs-6 py-3 px-4 textLightPurple">Become Our Trainer</button> *@
        </div>
        <div style="max-width: 45%;">
            <img src="~/images/MaskGroup.png" alt="Enrico Fermi at Chalkboard" class="img-fluid rounded-5 shadow-sm" style="opacity: 0.8;">
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container py-5 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-40 fw-bold textLightPurple pb-3">THINK ABOUT WHAT YOU CAN ACHIEVE</h2>
    <p class="text-22 fw-medium textGray pb-5">Set up online camps, let's carry the joy of learning with the community to the digital world. Don't miss this opportunity as the world becomes digital.</p>

    <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 row-cols-lg-3 g-4">
        <div class="col">
            <div class="p-4">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center rounded-3 mb-3" style="background-color: #FBD15B; width: 80px; height: 80px; margin: 0 auto;">
                    <i class="bi bi-laptop fs-2 textLightPurple"></i>
                </div>
                <h5 class="text-20 fw-bold textLightPurple mb-2">24/7 Online Education and Access</h5>
                <p class="text-16 fw-medium textGray">Completely create content according to your wishes, set up camps, upload videos. Set your pricing policy. Work with a monthly salary or a fee per course.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="p-4">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center rounded-3 mb-3" style="background-color: #FBD15B; width: 80px; height: 80px; margin: 0 auto;">
                    <i class="bi bi-journal-richtext fs-2 textLightPurple"></i>
                </div>
                <h5 class="text-20 fw-bold textLightPurple mb-2">Share Your Content</h5>
                <p class="text-16 fw-medium textGray">Share your academic work, articles, blog posts with the community. Earn income by charging for your e-books, pdf documents, or notes.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="p-4">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center rounded-3 mb-3" style="background-color: #FBD15B; width: 80px; height: 80px; margin: 0 auto;">
                    <i class="bi bi-people-fill fs-2 textLightPurple"></i>
                </div>
                <h5 class="text-20 fw-bold textLightPurple mb-2">Lead Your Community</h5>
                <p class="text-16 fw-medium textGray">Lead your own community, share your experiences and knowledge, and discover what successful, hardworking people who come together can achieve.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="p-4">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center rounded-3 mb-3" style="background-color: #FBD15B; width: 80px; height: 80px; margin: 0 auto;">
                    <i class="bi bi-currency-dollar fs-2 textLightPurple"></i>
                </div>
                <h5 class="text-20 fw-bold textLightPurple mb-2">Financial Return</h5>
                <p class="text-16 fw-medium textGray">All your efforts, your interaction with the community, and the effort you put in for its development will also provide a financial return for you.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="p-4">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center rounded-3 mb-3" style="background-color: #FBD15B; width: 80px; height: 80px; margin: 0 auto;">
                    <i class="bi bi-briefcase-fill fs-2 textLightPurple"></i>
                </div>
                <h5 class="text-20 fw-bold textLightPurple mb-2">Career Milestones</h5>
                <p class="text-16 fw-medium textGray">You will be helping people you have never met to climb their career milestones. Maybe you will work on the same project tomorrow. Are you in?</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="p-4">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center rounded-3 mb-3" style="background-color: #FBD15B; width: 80px; height: 80px; margin: 0 auto;">
                    <i class="bi bi-lightbulb-fill fs-2 textLightPurple"></i>
                </div>
                <h5 class="text-20 fw-bold textLightPurple mb-2">Develop Your Ideas</h5>
                <p class="text-16 fw-medium textGray">With the community, you will have the opportunity to develop your own ideas, turn them into projects, and reach a wider audience.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

